   "source": [
    "import gesture_processing\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "\n",
    "def label2vec(label):\n",
    "    result = np.zeros(4)\n",
    "    direction = label[8:]\n",
    "    if direction == 'Right':\n",
    "        result[0] = 1\n",
    "    elif direction == 'Left':\n",
    "        result[1] = 1\n",
    "    elif direction == 'Up':\n",
    "        result[2] = 1\n",
    "    elif direction == 'Down':\n",
    "        result[3] =1\n",
    "        \n",
    "    return result\n",
    "\n",
    "train = pd.read_csv('train-swipes',index_col = 0)\n",
    "test = pd.read_csv('test-swipes', index_col = 0)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "train_batch = np.zeros((1500,40,100,176))\n",
    "train_labels = np.zeros((1500,4))\n",
    "for i in range(1500):\n",
    "    train_batch[i] = gesture_processing.gest3D(train.iloc[i,0])\n",
    "    train_labels[i] = label2vec(train.iloc[i,1])\n",
    "train_batch = train_batch.reshape((1500,40,100,176,1))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 12,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import keras\n",
    "from keras.layers import Dense, Flatten, Conv3D, MaxPooling3D\n",
    "from keras.models import Sequential\n",
    "from keras.optimizers import Adam\n",
    "\n",
    "def test_model():\n",
    "    model = Sequential()\n",
    "    model.add(Flatten(input_shape=(40,100,176,1)))\n",
    "    model.add(Dense(100,activation = 'relu'))   \n",
    "    model.add(Dense(100,activation = 'relu')) \n",
    "    model.add(Dense(100,activation = 'relu')) \n",
    "    model.add(Dense(100,activation = 'relu')) \n",
    "    model.add(Dense(4,activation = 'softmax'))\n",
    "    model.compile(optimizer = 'adam',loss = 'categorical_crossentropy',metrics = ['accuracy'])\n",
    "    return model"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 14,
   "metadata": {},

      "Epoch 3/3\n",
      "1500/1500 [==============================] - 122s 81ms/step - loss: 11.9274 - acc: 0.2600\n"
     ]

    {

   ],
   "source": [
    "yo1 = test_model()\n",
    "yo1.fit(train_batch,train_labels,epochs = 3,batch_size = 10)"
   ]
